      "content": "it's hard to not be defined by it when it's all there is. everything i do just feels like i'm performing being a person, but the reality is just this emptiness. if everything is just going to keep being this painful and i'm never going to change, then what's even the point of fighting it anymore? it feels like fighting is just making the inevitable hurt more.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
